# Design Pro Max

- For landing pages, dashboards, redesigns, SaaS UI, marketing pages, design systems, Framer Motion, or high-polish UI work, read `.cursor/skills/design-pro-max/SKILL.md`.
- Start design work from product type, style, palette, typography, layout pattern, motion, accessibility, and responsive targets.
- Prefer SVG icons over emoji, visible focus states, contrast-safe colors, and `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- Use Framer Motion only in React/Next-compatible stacks; otherwise translate motion specs to the project animation system.
